<topic id="dcpp_how_to_remove_the_figure_nn_label">
    <title>How to Remove the Figure NN Label </title>
    <body>
    <p id="p_mkg_k5l_52c">For the <uicontrol keyref="pdf-html5-transformation"/> transformation
      scenario, the label for a table's title is wrapped in a span element with the class:
        <codeph>fig--title-label</codeph>.</p>
    <codeblock id="codeblock_qnq_k5l_52c" outputclass="language-xml">&lt;figure class="- topic/fig fig ">
  &lt;figcaption class="- topic/title title figcap">
    &lt;span class="figtitleprefix fig--title-label">Figure
      &lt;span class="fig--title-label-number">1&lt;/span>
      &lt;span class="fig--title-label-punctuation">. &lt;/span>
    &lt;/span>
    &lt;span class="fig--title">
      &lt;span class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ph title-wrapper">Lorem picsum&lt;/span>
    &lt;/span>
  &lt;/figcaption>
  ...
&lt;/figure></codeblock>
    <p id="p_tsk_l5l_52c">To hide it, set its display to none:</p>
    <codeblock id="codeblock_stv_l5l_52c" outputclass="language-css">.fig--title-label {
  display:none;
}</codeblock>
  </body>
</topic>
